{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Encoding API","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API\">Encoding API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>インターフェイス</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><strong>Encoding API</strong> はレガシーな非<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/UTF-8\">UTF-8</a>エンコーディングを含む様々な<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/character_encoding\">文字エンコーディング</a>のテキストを扱うメカニズムを提供します。</p>\n\n<p>このAPIは4つのインターフェースを提供します。それは、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a>、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a>、 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> そして <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"インターフェース","title":"インターフェース","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect2\">\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoderStream\"><code>TextDecoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoderStream\"><code>TextEncoderStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"チュートリアルとツール","title":"チュートリアルとツール","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://code.google.com/p/stringencoding/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">shim</a>はこのインターフェースをサポートしていないブラウザでもこのインターフェスを使えるようにします。</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Code_snippets/StringView\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays/StringView\"><code>StringView</code></a> はC言語の文字列配列型のような表現を提供します。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様書","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://encoding.spec.whatwg.org/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Encodingの仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">Encoding</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ブラウザーの対応","title":"ブラウザーの対応","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"TextDecoder","id":"textdecoder","isH3":true,"query":"api.TextDecoder","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"TextEncoder","id":"textencoder","isH3":true,"query":"api.TextEncoder","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API/bcd-2.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"インターフェース","id":"インターフェース"},{"text":"チュートリアルとツール","id":"チュートリアルとツール"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"ブラウザーの対応"}],"summary":"Encoding API はレガシーな非UTF-8エンコーディングを含む様々な文字エンコーディングのテキストを扱うメカニズムを提供します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"인코딩 API","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Encoding API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/encoding_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/encoding_api/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Encoding_API","title":"Encoding API"}],"pageTitle":"Encoding API - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}